&lt;li&gt;Available in basic or front flange mounting&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Adjustable stroke range: 10 mm (20 mm bore)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Adjustable stroke range: 15 mm (25 - 100 mm bore)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;External shock absorbers as standard&lt;/li&gt;
